13:15 Mose ni we wagerereye Abarubeni igihugu nk'uko amazu yabo ari.
13:16 Igihugu bahawe cyaheraga kuri Aroweri mu ruhande rw'ikibaya cya Arunoni, n'umudugudu wo hagati mu kibaya n'igitwa cyose cy'i Medeba
